# Package Manager

- Use pnpm instead of npm for all frontend dependencies
- Commands: `pnpm install`, `pnpm add <pkg>`, `pnpm dev`, etc.

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 with App Router and Turbopack
- TypeScript with strict mode enabled
- Tailwind CSS for all styling (no CSS modules, no styled-components)
- fal.ai OpenRouter with `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5` for AI
- Daytona for sandboxed code execution and file operations

## AI Integration

- All LLM calls go through fal.ai OpenRouter
- Endpoint: `openrouter/router` (NOT `fal-ai/any-llm`)
- Default model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`
- Use `@fal-ai/client` with `fal.subscribe("openrouter/router", { input: { model, prompt, system_prompt } })`
- Reference: https://fal.ai/models/openrouter/router
